ActIndian Act
SubjectOrder Granting the Transfer of Administration and Control of Eel River Indian Reserve No. 3 and Indian Ranch Indian Reserve, New Brunswick
PrecisOrder (1) authorizing the transfer from His Majesty to the province of New Brunswick of the administration and control of certain lands in Eel River Indian Reserve No. 3 and Indian Ranch Indian Reserve, New Brunswick; and (2) consenting to the exercise by His Majesty of the power to take the lands described in Schedule 1 for operating and maintaining a provincial public highway.
